674:    def run(self):
675-        """
676-        Run the job and immediately reschedule it.
677-        If the job's deadline is reached (configured using .until()), the job is not
678-        run and CancelJob is returned immediately. If the next scheduled run exceeds
679-        the job's deadline, CancelJob is returned after the execution. In this latter
680-        case CancelJob takes priority over any other returned value.
681-
